article.headline: Grigsby lifts Seattle U over Air Force 63-45
article.linkText: Grigsby lifts Seattle U over Air Force 63-45
article.story: LAS VEGAS -- — Riley Grigsby had 13 points to lead five Seattle University players in double figures as the Redhawks got past Air Force 63-45 on Sunday. Darrion Trammell, Rip Economou and Aaron Nettles added 12 points apiece for the Redhawks (3-0). Kobe Williamson chipped in 11 points. Glen McClintock had 11 points for the Falcons (1-1). ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
